high_descs: Turn around, then turn right and head towards the stove.
Pick up copper pot from the top left of the stove.
Turn right, then right again and head towards the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the copper pot inside the fridge, close it then open it, take the copper pot out and close the fridge.
Head to the cabinet under the microwave on the right.
Open cabinet under the microwave, put the copper pot inside and close it.
anns.task_desc: Take a cold copper pot to a cabinet.

high_descs: grab the pot off of the back left burner
put the pot in the fridge to cool, then take it out
bring the pot over to the fridge again
put it in the cabinet to the bottom right of the fridge
anns.task_desc: put a cooled pot in the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and move to the stove.
Pick up the pot that is on the left back side of the stove.
Turn all the way around and move to the fridge.
Open the fridge door.  Place the pot on the second shelf and shut the door.  Open the door and grab the pot on the second shelf.  Shut the door.
Move to the cabinet that is to the left of the fridge.
Open the cabinet.  Place the pot on the shelf.  Close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot in the fridge.
